Class Lab

  • java.lang.Object
    • entities.Lesson
      • entities.Lab
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Lab
extends Lesson
    Class Lab extends from Lesson, and is a specific type of lesson. It has no unique attributes of its own but implements the abstract functions provided by its parent, Lesson. Lab also imposes further constraints on the possible venues, and timings for the lesson.
